name: Jug Jugg Jeeyo
bio: A story set in the heart of Patiala and much like the city, it's full of love and laughter, colour and drama. This story is all about family and its values, unresolved yearnings and unexpected reconciliations. A good family entertainer

name: Bangarraju
bio: Bangarraju and Satyabhama come down to settle the life of their grandson Chinna Bangarraju and to save the treasure of temple.

name: Major
bio: The life of Maj. Sandeep Unnikrishnan, who fought against terrorists and was killed in action during the 2008 attacks at the Taj Palace Hotel in Mumbai, India.

name: CBI 5
bio: A series of murders is happening in the city. With the police failing to solve the case, a team of CBI Officers under CBI officer Sethurama Iyer take up the investigation to resolve the mystery.

name: Bachchhan Pandey
bio: A budding director tries to research a merciless gangster for making a film on gangster-ism. But her secret attempts to conduct the research fail when she gets caught for snooping.

name: Sardar Udham
bio: A biopic detailing the 2 decades that Punjabi Sikh revolutionary Udham Singh spent planning the assassination of the man responsible for the Jallianwala Bagh massacre.

name: Rehana Mariyam Noor
bio: An assistant professor at a local medical college, finds herself in a difficult position after witnessing a sexual assault where she knows both the victim and the perpetrator.

name: Dhaakad
bio: Agent Agni, a highly trained and deadly field agent is entrusted with the mission to gather Intel and eliminate Rudraveer, an international human and arms trafficker who has been off the radar for ten years.

name: Main Viyah Nahi Karona Tere Naal 2022
Kapil Sharma I'm Not Done Yet
Silence 2021 Can You Hear It Bollywood
Secret Superstar
bio: A talented teenage singer-songwriter living amid domestic abuse becomes a YouTube sensation after a video in which she hides her identity goes viral.
